10, body, male holotype (NCSU), dorsal view (total length 11.0 mm); 11, body, male holotype, lateral view; 12–18, male genitalia: 12, pygofer, lateral view; 13, valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; 1 4, styles and connective, dorsal view; 15, style, lateral view; 16, aedeagus, lateral view; 17, pair of apical processes of aedeagus, ventral view; 18, anal tube, lateral view. Scale bars: 12 = 2 mm; 13, 18 = 1 mm; 14–16 = 0.5 mm; 17 = 0.3 mm.
